01:35:38,337 --> 01:35:42,603
And years ago, I was riding back
from church with my family and

1586
01:35:42,675 --> 01:35:45,075
it was drizzling outside,
and I had a thought.

1587
01:35:45,144 --> 01:35:49,740
Why couldn't a wiper
work like an eyelid?

1588
01:35:52,818 --> 01:35:55,218
Why couldn't it blink?

1589
01:35:58,223 --> 01:36:00,123
That's how I came up with it.

